summary.span: 封装 HTTP 内部对象，该对象提供对会话状态值、会话级别设置和生存期管理方法的访问。

span.span: Encapsulates the HTTP intrinsic object that provides access to session-state values, session-level settings, and lifetime management methods.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 类派生自 类，用作类的包装 。The class derives from the class and serves as a wrapper for the class. 此类公开类的功能 并公开 类型。This class exposes the functionality of the class and exposes the type. 类可让你将应用程序中类的原始实现替换为 自定义实现，例如在 ASP.NET 管道之外执行单元测试时。The class lets you replace the original implementation of the class in your application with a custom implementation, such as when you perform unit testing outside the ASP.NET pipeline.
